  "detailed_description": "ZEROCRON is a straightforward, classical arcade Twin-Stick Shoot-Em-Up with a strong Commodore-Amiga-era feel.<br><br>Blast asteroids and enemies to burning pixeldust!<br><br>Developed and polished for 10 years.<br><br>-99 levels with increasing difficulty<br>-no lives, just see how far you can survive the action<br>-automatically saves at every level for casual play<br>-buy multiple weapons and upgrades in shop<br>-various enemies and bosses<br>-homemade pixel-gfx<br>-4 difficulty settings<br>-keyboard/mouse and joypad-support<br>-arcade (MAME) compatible controlmode<br><br>No Bullet Hell, no RPG, no roguelike, no fancy twists ;)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/31ddd267b3cdeb5b9fc0e227d0fad9f6.poster.avif?t=1655033837\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/31ddd267b3cdeb5b9fc0e227d0fad9f6.webm?t=1655033837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/31ddd267b3cdeb5b9fc0e227d0fad9f6.mp4?t=1655033837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/4359c0a5f1332d5a4c545a856311d2fb.poster.avif?t=1655033837\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/4359c0a5f1332d5a4c545a856311d2fb.webm?t=1655033837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/4359c0a5f1332d5a4c545a856311d2fb.mp4?t=1655033837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "ZEROCRON is a straightforward, classical arcade Twin-Stick Shoot-Em-Up with a strong Commodore-Amiga-era feel.<br><br>Blast asteroids and enemies to burning pixeldust!<br><br>Developed and polished for 10 years.<br><br>-99 levels with increasing difficulty<br>-no lives, just see how far you can survive the action<br>-automatically saves at every level for casual play<br>-buy multiple weapons and upgrades in shop<br>-various enemies and bosses<br>-homemade pixel-gfx<br>-4 difficulty settings<br>-keyboard/mouse and joypad-support<br>-arcade (MAME) compatible controlmode<br><br>No Bullet Hell, no RPG, no roguelike, no fancy twists ;)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/31ddd267b3cdeb5b9fc0e227d0fad9f6.poster.avif?t=1655033837\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/31ddd267b3cdeb5b9fc0e227d0fad9f6.webm?t=1655033837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/31ddd267b3cdeb5b9fc0e227d0fad9f6.mp4?t=1655033837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/4359c0a5f1332d5a4c545a856311d2fb.poster.avif?t=1655033837\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/4359c0a5f1332d5a4c545a856311d2fb.webm?t=1655033837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1964580/extras/4359c0a5f1332d5a4c545a856311d2fb.mp4?t=1655033837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
